p: \bI guess it's down to the four of us.
\bThe Infernal Cult works from here. This is where the broadcast signal came from.
\bIt's like a maze in there, we have to be careful.
\bWe'll split up, two groups of two. One gym leader, one kid.
\bNora, you're with me.\n\pn, you can go with Diana.
\bThe main priority is finding a way to reverse whatever mind control he's got the region in.
\bBut if you see Zenith, get him. There's no way he should last against two legend-users, no matter how strong he is.
\b...let's go. Don't get caught. Don't be dumb.
\r...oohhhh boy. This isn't dangerous at all.
\rLet's go. As long as we're careful, and more importantly, quiet , we'll be fine.\nWe'll meet up with them and... yeah. Hopefully.
